c-dung-gi-lam-dep-da-giam-can-chua-dau-da-day-8.jpg\\\" style=\\\"width: 600px; height: 371px;\\\" \\/>\\r\\n<p>Tinh b\\u1ed9t ngh\\u1ec7 b&ecirc;n c\\u1ea1nh vi\\u1ec7c l&agrave;m \\u0111\\u1eb9p c&ograve;n gi&uacute;p ch\\u0103m s&oacute;c s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe to&agrave;n di\\u1ec7n t\\u1eeb trong ra ngo&agrave;i. \\u0110\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t u\\u1ed1ng tinh b\\u1ed9t ngh\\u1ec7 m\\u1eadt ong c&ograve;n l&agrave;m da tr\\u1eafng h\\u1ed3ng, gi\\u1ea3m m\\u1ee5n, gi&uacute;p da m\\u1ecbn m&agrave;ng, l&agrave;m m\\u1edd s\\u1eb9o v&agrave; th&acirc;m hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3; \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi h\\u1ed7 ch\\u1eefa tr\\u1ecb vi&ecirc;m lo&eacute;t d\\u1ea1 d&agrave;y c\\u1ef1c t\\u1ed1t. Th\\u1ebf th&igrave; vi&ecirc;n ngh\\u1ec7 m\\u1eadt ong c&oacute; t&aacute;c d\\u1ee5ng g&igrave;? C&ugrave;ng t&igrave;m hi\\u1ec3u nh&eacute;.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>M\\u1eadt ong ch\\u1ee9a 13-20% l&agrave; n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, 75-80% hydrat cacbon; r\\u1ea5t nhi\\u1ec1u vitamin nh\\u01b0: B1, B2, B6, E, K, C, ti\\u1ec1n t\\u1ed1 vitamin A, a xit folic&hellip; H\\u01a1n n\\u1eefa c&ograve;n ch\\u1ee9a \\u0111\\u1ef1ng h\\u01a1n 300 vi ch\\u1ea5t gi&uacute;p b\\u1ed5 sung m\\u1ecdi nguy&ecirc;n t\\u1ed1 vi l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng, nhi\\u1ec1u vitamin, a xit v&agrave; men ti&ecirc;u h&oacute;a c\\u1ea7n thi\\u1ebft cho c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3 nh\\u1eb1m k&iacute;ch th&iacute;ch s\\u1ef1 trao \\u0111\\u1ed5i ch\\u1ea5t n&ecirc;n v\\u1eeba l&agrave;m thu\\u1ed1c b\\u1ed5 d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng v\\u1eeba c&oacute; t&aacute;c d\\u1ee5ng kh&aacute;ng khu\\u1ea9n hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3.<br \\/>\\r\\n<img alt=\\\"vien nghe mat ong\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/thuhienstore.club\\/documents\\/photos\\/vien-nghe-mat-ong-co-tac-dung-gi-lam-dep-da-giam-can-chua-dau-da-day-9.jpg\\\" style=\\\"width: 600px; height: 337px;\\\" \\/><br \\/>\\r\\n&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>H\\u01a1n n\\u1eefa ho\\u1ea1t ch\\u1ea5t kali v&agrave; magi&ecirc; c&oacute; trong m\\u1eadt ong c&ograve;n gi&uacute;p k&iacute;ch th&iacute;ch h\\u1ec7 ti&ecirc;u h&oacute;a, gi&uacute;p \\u0103n ngon mi\\u1ec7ng h\\u01a1n v&agrave; c&ograve;n gi&uacute;p t\\u0103ng kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng mi\\u1ec5n d\\u1ecbch, l&agrave;m gi\\u1ea3m ti\\u1ebft a xit v&agrave; tri\\u1ec7u ch\\u1ee9ng \\u0111au r&aacute;t nhanh ch&oacute;ng.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><strong>1. Vi&ecirc;n ngh\\u1ec7 m\\u1eadt ong c&oacute; t&aacute;c d\\u1ee5ng gi&uacute;p da s&aacute;ng \\u0111\\u1eb9p<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Tinh b\\u1ed9t ngh\\u1ec7 gi&uacute;p \\u0111i\\u1ec1u tr\\u1ecb c&aacute;c v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1 m\\u1ee5n, n&aacute;m, t&agrave;n nhang, \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng \\u1ea9m cho da, gi\\u1ea3m n\\u1ebfp nh\\u0103n, ng\\u0103n ng\\u1eeba l&atilde;o ho&aacute;, tr\\u1ecb r\\u1ea1n da,&hellip;.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>B\\u1ea1n s\\u1ebd b\\u1ea5t ng\\u1edd v\\u1edbi c&ocirc;ng d\\u1ee5ng l&agrave;m \\u0111\\u1eb9p c\\u1ee7a tinh b\\u1ed9t ngh\\u1ec7. Kh&ocirc;ng ch\\u1ec9 u\\u1ed1ng \\u0111\\u01a1n thu\\u1ea7n m&agrave; c&ograve;n l&agrave;m m\\u1eb7t n\\u1ea1 \\u0111\\u1ec3 d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng da m\\u1eb7t v&agrave; d\\u1ea1 to&agrave;n th&acirc;n.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><strong>2. Vi&ecirc;n ngh\\u1ec7 m\\u1eadt ong c&oacute; t&aacute;c d\\u1ee5ng gi\\u1ea3m c&acirc;n an to&agrave;n<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Tinh b\\u1ed9t ngh\\u1ec7 gi&uacute;p chuy\\u1ec3n h&oacute;a ch\\u1ea5t b&eacute;o th&agrave;nh n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi m\\u1ee1 th\\u1eeba gi\\u1ea3m \\u0111i m\\u1ed9t c&aacute;ch an to&agrave;n. Ngh\\u1ec7 c&oacute; t&aacute;c d\\u1ee5ng \\u0111\\u1ed1t ch&aacute;y m\\u1ee1 th\\u1eeba trong c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3, ng\\u0103n s\\u1ef1 h\\u1ea5p th\\u1ee5 ch\\u1ea5t b&eacute;o trong c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Khi th\\u1eeba c&acirc;n b&eacute;o ph&igrave; b\\u1ea1n c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng tinh b\\u1ed9t ngh\\u1ec7 h&ograve;a v\\u1edbi n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u1ea5m v&agrave; cho th&ecirc;m ch&uacute;t \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng ho\\u1eb7c m\\u1eadt ong \\u0111\\u1ec3 ph\\u1ee5c v\\u1ee5 qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh gi\\u1ea3m c&acirc;n c\\u1ee7a m&igrave;nh.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><strong>3. Vi&ecirc;n ngh\\u1ec7 m\\u1eadt ong t\\u1ed1t cho ph\\u1ee5 n\\u1eef sau sinh<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Curcumin ch\\u1ed1ng nhi\\u1ec5m khu\\u1ea9n, kh&ocirc;ng ra m&aacute;u h&ocirc;i sau sinh v&agrave; gi&uacute;p v\\u1ebft m\\u1ed5 t\\u1ea7ng sinh m&ocirc;n mau l&agrave;nh. \\u1ed4n \\u0111\\u1ecbnh d\\u1ea1 d&agrave;y, gi\\u1ea3m thi\\u1ec3u r\\u1ea1n da, t&agrave;n nhang, tan m\\u1ee1 th\\u1eeba \\u1edf b\\u1ee5ng, \\u0111&ugrave;i. Gi&uacute;p ch\\u1ecb em l\\u1ea5y l\\u1ea1i v&oacute;c d&aacute;ng thon g\\u1ecdn.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Khi u\\u1ed1ng tinh b\\u1ed9t ngh\\u1ec7 gi&uacute;p ph\\u1ee5 n\\u1eef sau sinh nhanh ch&oacute;ng ph\\u1ee5c h\\u1ed3i s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe nhanh ch&oacute;ng, gi&uacute;p tan huy\\u1ebft \\u1ee9, gi&uacute;p t\\u1eed cung nhanh li\\u1ec1n s\\u1eb9o. Kh&ocirc;ng ch\\u1ec9 gi&uacute;p ph\\u1ee5c h\\u1ed3i s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe sau sinh nhanh ch&oacute;ng m&agrave; c&ograve;n l&agrave;m \\u0111\\u1eb9p da sau sinh, l&agrave;m gi\\u1ea3m m\\u1ee1 th\\u1eeba sau sinh.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>U\\u1ed1ng tinh b\\u1ed9t ngh\\u1ec7 m\\u1eadt ong gi&uacute;p l&agrave;m&nbsp;<strong>ti&ecirc;u m\\u1ee1 sau sinh hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3<\\/strong>. Ph&ograve;ng tr&aacute;nh h\\u1eadu s\\u1ea3n, mau l&agrave;nh v\\u1ebft m\\u1ed5, v\\u1ebft r\\u1ea1ch, ch\\u1ed1ng vi&ecirc;m nhi\\u1ec5m t\\u1ea7ng sinh m&ocirc;n. Ch\\u1ed1ng r\\u1ee5ng t&oacute;c v&agrave; l&agrave;m d&agrave;y t&oacute;c. Gi&uacute;p da tr\\u1eafng h\\u1ed3ng, tr\\u1ebb ho&aacute; da, \\u0111i\\u1ec1u tr\\u1ecb m\\u1ee5n &ndash; th&acirc;m &ndash; n&aacute;m sau sinh. T\\u0103ng ti\\u1ebft s\\u1eefa cho m\\u1eb9 sau sinh.<br \\/>\\r\\n<img alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/thuhienstore.club\\/documents\\/photos\\/z1392406460311_3faa7eaddc020ac07e13af9821fffac3.jpg\\\" style=\\\"width: 600px; height: 800px;\\\" \\/><br \\/>\\r\\n&nbsp;<\\/