t_300-300-150x150.png\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://webico.r.worldssl.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/cfa6140fd326968c9e06e5cc5cc0cf9f_number-three-green-square-number-10-green-clipart_300-300-150x150.png 150w, https://webico.r.worldssl.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/cfa6140fd326968c9e06e5cc5cc0cf9f_number-three-green-square-number-10-green-clipart_300-300.png 300w, https://webico.r.worldssl.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/cfa6140fd326968c9e06e5cc5cc0cf9f_number-three-green-square-number-10-green-clipart_300-300-180x180.png 180w\" data-was-processed=\"true\" height=\"29\" sizes=\"(max-width: 30px) 100vw, 30px\" src=\"https://webico.r.worldssl.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/cfa6140fd326968c9e06e5cc5cc0cf9f_number-three-green-square-number-10-green-clipart_300-300-150x150.png\" srcset=\"https://webico.r.worldssl.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/cfa6140fd326968c9e06e5cc5cc0cf9f_number-three-green-square-number-10-green-clipart_300-300-150x150.png 150w, https://webico.r.worldssl.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/cfa6140fd326968c9e06e5cc5cc0cf9f_number-three-green-square-number-10-green-clipart_300-300.png 300w, https://webico.r.worldssl.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/cfa6140fd326968c9e06e5cc5cc0cf9f_number-three-green-square-number-10-green-clipart_300-300-180x180.png 180w\" width=\"30\" />: Dựa v&agrave;o y&ecirc;u cầu điều chỉnh của kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng, John Nguyen Team điều chỉnh lần 2 &ndash; tối đa 2 lần (3 ng&agrave;y)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bước&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" data-lazy-src=\"https://webico.r.worldssl.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/number4_PNG15027-150x150.png\" data-was-processed=\"true\" height=\"28\" src=\"https://webico.r.worldssl.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/number4_PNG15027-150x150.png\" width=\"31\" />: Hai b&ecirc;n chốt giao diện cuối c&ugrave;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Giai đoạn 3:&nbsp;</strong>Lập tr&igrave;nh website v&agrave; chức năng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bước&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" data-lazy-src=\"https://webico.r.worldssl.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/dcbc9043d9